msgid ""
"When running the `lv_demo_benchmark` from LVGL the user can compare the "
"performance when the PPA is enabled versus the pure software rendering, "
"by using the latest version of the LVGL and LVGL port component it can be"
" observed an average saving of 30% of the rendering time for draw tasks "
