#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/integration/chip_vendors/stm32/ltdc.rst:105
msgid ""
"You should ensure the LTDC framebuffer memory is actually reserved in the"
" linker script. This is a file that normally has the extension ``.ld``. "
