msgstr "``all``: File indipendenti dall'architettura."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/integration/embedded_linux/os/yocto/lvgl_recipe.rst:237
msgid "``cortexa53``: Files for the Cortex-A53 (ARMv8-A) architecture."
