#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/integration/overview/configuration.rst:18
msgid ""
"When setting up your project for the first time, copy "
"``lvgl/lv_conf_template.h`` to ``lv_conf.h`` next to the ``lvgl`` folder."
