#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/integration/rtos/zephyr.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Small** - Runs on microcontrollers as small as 8 kB Flash and 5 kB of "
"RAM."
msgstr "**Piccolo** - Funziona su microcontrollori con soli 8 kB di Flash e 5 kB di RAM."

#: ../../lvgl/docs/intermediate/integration/rtos/zephyr.rst:25
